Logbook Konni for OpenCPN
==========================

Building from source
--------------------
Clone the git repository to <OPENCPN_SOURCE_TLD>/plugins/LogbookKonni_pi (the _pi at the end matters!)
cd <OPENCPN_SOURCE_TLD>/plugins
git clone git://github.com/konnibe/LogbookKonni.git LogbookKonni_pi

if You want to compile the plugin with the latest 2.6 Beta of OpenCPN please change in the file "logbook_pi.h" the line

#define     MY_API_VERSION_MINOR    5 // for OpenCPN 2.5
#define     MY_API_VERSION_MINOR    6 // for OpenCPN 2.6 Beta

Build OpenCPN as normally (build instructions on http://opencpn.org)

Localizations distribution
--------------------------
OpenCPN_Logbook_Languages.zip
The .mo files belong to the respective directory structure
eg. 
de\LC_MESSAGES\opencpn-logbookkonni_pi.mo
es\LC_MESSAGES\opencpn-logbookkonni_pi.mo
etc.

Layouts distribution
--------------------
Zip the contents of data\Layouts into OpenCPN_Logbook_Layouts.zip
